    dc:description "Figure 62. Urupelma veronicae sp. n. from Peru, Cusco, Abra Málaga near Nevado Veronica, 4450 m a. s.l., habitus of male paratype (MUSM-ENT 0513018), dorsal view. Photo: R. Kaderka." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10492134/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10492156>
    dc:description "Figure 70. A. Urupelma dianae sp. n. from Peru, Cusco, between Phiry near Ollantaytambo and Abra Málaga, 3874 m a.s.l., habitus of male paratype (MUSM-ENT 0513016), dorsal view. B. Natural habitat. Photo: R. Kaderka." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10492156/files/figure.png" ;
