<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10492158>
    dc:description "Figure 71. Urupelma dianae sp. n. from Peru, Cusco, between Phiry near Ollantaytambo and Abra Málaga. A. Adult female with egg sac, dorsal view. B. Adult female with juveniles, dorsal view. Photo: R. Kaderka." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10492158/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10492160>
    dc:description "Figure 72. Urupelma dianae sp. n., male holotype (MUSM-ENT 0513017) from Peru, Cusco, between Phiry near Ollantaytambo and Abra Málaga., 3868 m a.s.l. A. Carapace, coxae and trochantera, dorsal view. B. Sternum, labium, maxillae and coxae, ventral view. C. Ocular tubercle, dorsal view. D. Labium and left maxilla, ventral view. E. Palpal tibia, retrolateral view. F. Abdomen, dorsal view. G. Abdomen, ventral view. Scale bar = 1 mm. Photo: R. Kaderka." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10492160/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10492162>
    dc:description "Figure 73. Urupelma dianae sp. n., male holotype (MUSM-ENT 0513017) from Peru, Cusco, between Phiry near Ollantaytambo and Abra Málaga., 3868 m a.s.l. A. Palpal tibia, dorsal view. B. Palpal tibia, ventral view. C. Left tibia I, prolaterally ventral view. Scale bar = 1 mm. Photo: R. Kaderka." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10492162/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10492164>
    dc:description "Figure 74. Urupelma dianae sp. n., male holotype (MUSM-ENT 0513017) from Peru, Cusco, between Phiry near Ollantaytambo and Abra Málaga., 3868 m a.s.l., morphology of right palpal bulb. A. Prolateral view. B. Retrolateral view. C. Dorsal view. Large arrow shows sperm pore, short arrow shows small oval lobe at the distal end of PI keel. D. Ventral view. Scale bar = 1 mm. Photo: R. Kaderka." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10492164/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10492168>
    dc:description "Figure 75. Urupelma dianae sp. n. from Peru, Cusco, between Phiry near Ollantaytambo and Abra Málaga., 3868 m a.s.l. A–F. Morphology of female spermathecae dissected from exuviae collected in situ. Scale bar = 1 mm. Photo: R. Kaderka." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10492168/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10492170>
    dc:description "Figure 76. Distribution map of Urupelma gen. n. from Peru. Prepared by M. Hüsser." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10492170/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10492172>
    dc:description "Figure 77. Distribution map of Urupelma spp. from Urubamba River Valley, Cusco, Peru, showing highly diversified populations and so-called ‘high mountain insularisation̍ caused by geographical barriers and restricted gene flow. Red square = Urupelma peruvianum (Chamberlin, 1916) and Urupelma sanctitheresae sp. n. from Santa Teresa, Cusco; white square = Urupelma peruvianum (Chamberlin, 1916) and Urupelma sanctimariae sp. n. from Santa María, Cusco; yellow square = Urupelma machiguenga sp. n. from Echarati, Cusco; green square = Urupelma veronicae sp. n. from Abra Málaga near Nevado Veronica, Cusco; pink square = Urupelma dianae sp. n. from between Phiry near Ollantaytambo and Abra Málaga, Cusco. Scale bar: 10 km. Prepared by R. Kaderka." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10492172/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

